      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>wholewheat noodles </strong>to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles, then set aside to soak for 4 min</p><p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a very high heat</p><p>Drain your<strong> tofu</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p><p>Cut the<strong> tofu</strong> in half and then cut each half into thick strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1988.-step-3.2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1988.-step-3.2-x400.jpg",
