        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is crisp, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>sticky sauce</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min further until sticky and caramelised</p><p>Once caramelised, add your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 30 secs further, or until slightly loosened – this is your <strong>sticky sesame tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1988.-step-6.2-x200.jpg",
